    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enter <strong>Mobspawn</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152960/extras/7a366b76f96db82e8544cbaf51292cfa.gif?t=1754967220\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152960/extras/7a366b76f96db82e8544cbaf51292cfa.poster.avif?t=1754967220\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relentless isometric gauntlet where every floor tests your wit and reflexes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with a vacuum and your ingenuity, repurpose the environment itself as your ordnance.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fling furniture, debris, and the scraps of dispatched foes to clear your path to the elevator.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and scavenge for upgrades to improve your abilities... you'll need it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>How high will you ascend?</i></p>",
